| 5.2 | Build Executive Summary card | 0.5 days | |
| 5.3 | Build standard chart components (bar, stacked bar, histogram) | 2 days | Use a charting library (Recharts, Chart.js, or similar) |
| 5.4 | Build Question Result Card with chart/table toggle | 1 day | |
| 5.5 | Build cross-tabulation dropdown + grouped bar rendering | 1.5 days | |
| 5.6 | Build significance testing display (asterisks, letter notation) | 0.5 days | |
| 5.7 | Build Van Westendorp specialty chart | 1 day | 4-line intersection chart |
| 5.8 | Build Gabor-Granger specialty chart | 0.5 days | Demand curve |
| 5.9 | Build AI insight callout per question | 0.5 days | |
| 5.10 | Create seed data for Pricing Study | 1 day | Must be statistically realistic |
| 5.11 | Create seed data for Message Testing | 0.5 days | |
| 5.12 | Create seed data for Concept Testing | 0.5 days | |
| 5.13 | Build PDF export | 1 day | |
| 5.14 | Build PPTX export | 1.5 days | Use pptx library |
| 5.15 | End-to-end test with all 3 seed datasets | 1 day | |

