### Specifications

- **Position**: Fixed top, full width, height 56px
- **Background**: White, bottom border 1px `#E5E7EB`
- **Left**: App logo/wordmark (placeholder â€” "SurveyEngine" or your actual brand). Links to Dashboard.
- **Center-left**: Top-level nav links:
  - "Home" â†’ Dashboard (`/`)
  - "My Studies" â†’ Dashboard (`/`) â€” same destination, but when inside a project this becomes the breadcrumb root
- **Right**: User avatar / initials circle (placeholder for auth â€” not functional in MVP, but reserves the space)
- **Breadcrumb row** (second line, only shown when inside a project):
  - Format: `My Studies â€º [Project Name] â€º [Current Page]`
  - Each segment is a link except the current page (which is bold, non-linked)
  - Project name links to the most recent stage of that project
  - Breadcrumb height: 32px, 13px text, color `#6B7280`, active segment `#111827`

---

## Page 0: Dashboard

### Purpose
Central hub for all projects. Shows existing studies and their status. Entry point to create new studies.

