### Updated Build Order

```
Phase 0:  Global nav + Dashboard + Routing          (foundation)
Phase 1a: Setup page                                 (entry point)
Phase 1b: Survey Skills updates                      (generation engine)
Phase 2:  LOI Functionality                          (wired into setup + editor)
Phase 3:  Edit Function                              (editor page)
Phase 4:  Test / Preview                             (preview page)
Phase 5:  Reporting                                  (report page)
Phase 6:  Launch                                     (launch wizard + status page)
```

Build the navigation shell and setup page first â€” this gives you a working front door and lets you demo the brief-to-survey generation flow early, even before the editor is built.

