```

### What Each State Unlocks

| State | Accessible Pages | Primary CTA |
|-------|-----------------|-------------|
| DRAFT (brief only) | Dashboard, Setup | "Generate Survey" |
| DRAFT (has survey) | Dashboard, Setup, Editor, Preview | "Launch" (in editor header) |
| LIVE | Dashboard, Setup (read-only), Editor (read-only), Status | "View Status" |
| COMPLETED | Dashboard, Setup (read-only), Editor (read-only), Report | "View Report" |

### Breadcrumb Behavior Per Page

| Page | Breadcrumb |
|------|-----------|
| Dashboard | (none â€” this is the root) |
| Setup (new) | My Studies â€º New Study |
| Setup (existing) | My Studies â€º [Project Name] â€º Brief |
| Editor | My Studies â€º [Project Name] â€º Editor |
| Preview | My Studies â€º [Project Name] â€º Preview |
| Launch | My Studies â€º [Project Name] â€º Launch |
| Status | My Studies â€º [Project Name] â€º Status |
| Report | My Studies â€º [Project Name] â€º Report |